# Tauri icons (placeholders are generated by build.rs; real ones via
# `pnpm tauri icon`. After generating real icons run:
#   git add -f src-tauri/icons/icon.ico src-tauri/icons/*.png ...
src-tauri/icons/*.ico
src-tauri/icons/*.icns
src-tauri/icons/*.png
!src-tauri/icons/README.md

